intro text: You’re about to use a short (3 min), safe and anonymous health checkup. Your answers will be carefully analyzed and you’ll learn about possible causes of your symptoms.
terms text: Before using the checkup, please read Terms of Service. Remember that:
terms 1: Checkup is not a diagnosis. Checkup is for informational purposes and is not a qualified medical opinion.
terms 2: Do not use in emergencies. In case of health emergency, call your local emergency number immediately.
terms 3: Your data is safe. Information that you provide is anonymous and not shared with anyone.
